title: NFL Preseason Week 2 Recap, Fantasy Draft Weekend Preview (Football 08/17)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson of CBS Sports to break down the action from the three preseason games on Thursday night, including the Nick Foles injury, James Washington's impressive performance and what the Jets will do with Teddy Bridgewater and Sam Darnold. Then, Heath Cummings joins the show to break down what he's looking for over the weekend of preseason games to help get everyone prepared for their fantasy drafts. Will also laments his Jets preseason loss but gears back up with another lock.
